flowRoot.flowPara: Q: what are the test profiles for?

text.tspan: Calibration will create a new color profile.
This will be used if you export the profile to be used on
This will be used if you export the profile to be used on
Calibration will produce a profile that you can use to color
manage your device. The longer you spend on calibration, the
better the quality of the color profile.
You can use a color profile on multiple computers, or even
create profiles for different lighting conditions.
